title: Tiny Desk Contest Top Shelf: Our Favorite 2021 Entries, Episode 1
description: Before we announce this year's Tiny Desk Contest winner, we're asking our judges to share their favorite entries in a weekly livestreamed series. First up: Tiny Desk producer Bobby Carter.
